      <h1 class="mt-2 text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight">How to Pass the Barber State Board Exam on Your First Try</h1>
      <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-300 max-w-2xl">
        Practical advice from someone who's been there — long before the classroom. No fluff — just what actually helps.
